1. *Kartica* je bila odbijena kada sam pokušao da je koristim u prodavnici. (*Kartica* - The card was declined when I tried to use it in the store.)
2. Imam više *kartica* u novčaniku, ali ne znam koju da koristim. ( *Kartica* - I have several cards in my wallet, but I don't know which one to use.)
3. Molim vas, pokažite mi vašu *karticu* identiteta. (*Karticu* - Please show me your identity *card*.)
4. Kada sam pretraživao internet, pronašao sam mnogo različitih vrsta *kartica*. (*Kartica* - When I searched the internet, I found many different types of *cards*.)
5. U banci sam morao potpisati nekoliko *kartica* pre nego što sam dobio kredit. (*Kartica* - At the bank, I had to sign several *cards* before I got the loan.)
6. Da li ste primili svoju novu kreditnu *karticu*? (*Karticu* - Have you received your new credit *card*?)
7. *Kartice* za pozivnice su već naručene za venčanje. (*Kartice* - The invitation *cards* have already been ordered for the wedding.)
8. Pogrešno sam unela PIN kod na *kartici* i sada ne mogu da podignem novac. (*Kartici* - I entered the wrong PIN code on the *card* and now I can't withdraw money.)